title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Apr 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Apr 15 2022
description:
Biden shakes hands with nobody, lies about Putin causing inflation. Clay says: "Every time we play a cut of Joe Biden speaking, he sounds worse." Buck says Biden's never been up for the presidency and it's embarrassing for the country. CNN on Biden's approval rating, which has fallen to 33% in Quinnipiac poll. Biden covid czar blames masking kids on the CDC. Twitter board rejects bid, DOJ and SEC go after Musk. Psaki says Fox's Peter Doocy sounds like a stupid SOB.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
